* [https://web.mit.edu/multics-history/source/Multics/ldd/system_library_unbundled/object/binaries/bound_emacs_full_.archive bound_emacs_full_.archive]
* [https://web.mit.edu/multics-history/source/Multics/ldd/system_library_unbundled/object/binaries/bound_emacs_full_.archive.9 bound_emacs_full_.archive.9]
* [https://web.mit.edu/multics-history/source/Multics/ldd/system_library_unbundled/object/binaries/bound_emacs_macros_.archive bound_emacs_macros_.archive]
* [https://web.mit.edu/multics-history/source/Multics/ldd/system_library_unbundled/object/binaries/bound_emacs_macros_.archive.9 bound_emacs_macros_.archive.9]
