----

Looks like BarryMargolin made lots of changes to Multics Emacs.  You can also find a listing of his work on Multics Emacs on the [https://multicians.org/multicians.html Multicians.org] site.

For more information, see Greenberg's paper, [http://www.multicians.org/mepap.html "Multics Emacs: The History, Design and Implementation"].

